title: Exploratory Visulization For DSC106
description: Design and create an exploratory visualization based on data gathered on weather patterns in various cities in America. Created for DSC 106, attempted to effectively communicate a clear idea and story behind the data provided to us. Also provided clear rationale for every design choice made in the project.

title: Recipes and Ratings For DSC80
description: Comprehensive project for DSC80 that includes missingness analysis, creating a predictive model, hypothesis testing, and more. This project utilized all of the skills I learned in DSC80 and the result is a story that dives into how I can try and predict cooking time based on calories and other nutritional information.
